claim.claim-text:
1. A gaming system method using a wireless communication device, including the steps of: 
providing call data identifying a gaming system player; 
initiating a call from the wireless communication device through a telephone cell network to a financial center; 
requesting a cash transfer, based on said call data, credited to said wireless communication device, and receiving said cash transfer of a predetermined cash balance; 
communicating, using said wireless communication device, with a casino to transfer a portion of the predetermined cash balance from the wireless communication device to the credit of a particular gaming machine; and 
playing the particular gaming machine using the portion of cash balance so transferred.

9. A gaming system method using a wireless communication device, including the steps of: 
providing call data identifying a gaming system player; 
initiating a call from the wireless communication device through a telephone cell network to a financial center; 
requesting a cash transfer, based on said call data and using said wireless communication device, credited to a casino on behalf of the gaming system player, to provide a predetermined cash balance; 
communicating, using said wireless communication device, with the casino to allocate at least a portion of the predetermined cash balance to a particular gaming machine; and 
playing the particular gaming machine using the portion of cash balance so transferred.

20. A gaming system method using a communication device including the steps of: 
providing call data identifying a gaming system player; 
initiating a call from the communication device through a telephone network to a financial center; 
requesting a cash transfer, based on said call data, credited to a casino on behalf of the gaming system player, or to the communication device, to provide a predetermined cash balance; 
communicating, using said communication device, with the casino to allocate at least a portion of the predetermined cash balance to a particular gaming machine; and 
playing the particular gaming machine using a portion of cash balance so transferred.
